es here but sort of rant!</span><hr size=1> I've been reading over the proposed changes for the enchanter class that they want to go over on EQcastersrealm.<br>
I have to say this somewhere my post didn't make the cut off on the Eq boards. BUT WTF!?!?! what it seems like to me is a bunch of 20 - 30th level enchanters saw what enchanters at level 50+ were doing and got jealous. I happen to beleive our class is well balanced .. there's just enough chance of me not being about to do anything as there is for me to pull off the miraculous!!! I do agree we are given the title illusionist but I can let that ride on something else because it's really not part of the game .. mainly becuase they have taken the usefulness of Illusions from us by giving others illusions and then saying WHOA! we can't have everyone with and illusion be able to do what an enchanter does oh wait we'll just take that from enchanters as well .. there goes 2 lines of spells. <br>
Speaking of spell lines - Lull - PLEASE REMOVE THIS FROM OUR LIST OF SPELLS - we get enough every level to toss in the back of our book and labelled NEVER USE OR IT WILL KILL YOU SPELLS .. this line takes the cake .. oh btw thanks for the cap on debuffs it does really work good but can't really thank you because it's still not what it should be.<br>
...<br>
...<br>
Ok .. I'm done but all in all I think the enchanter class is well balanced there is a give in take in the class. Yes the essential enchanter deal needs to be changed a bit .. I need sleep too damn it! oh and I've seen people ask for a nerf to the mez line enchanters get . .. next time you think it should be mez'd follow an enchanter around and watch the casts sometime!<br>
...<br>
...<br>
Ok done .. just a few cents on it .. btw all the BS that they want to do to Chanters are:<br>
1. Things that have been wrong since beta.<br>
2. Things that have been wrong since Kunark.<br>
3. Things to make our job easier other than %t is mez'd .. do not see a bonus here.<br>
4. they want charmed pets to have a different color .. hell you work that out in group and you need not worry.<br>
5. change sex .. we have enough of that without having a class that can do it!<br>
6. morph into this morph into that - well ya know you'd think illusionist meant master of illusions but apparently it means you can illusion any creature that isn't in this hate table! .. I don't know for sure but I have an IQ higher than that of a dorf even if it is a snow dorf!! He should not see through my illusion .. it IS an illusion right? BAH!! OK done<br>
